Disk & Memory
==========

df -h â†’ du -sh â†’ free -m â†’ lsblk â†’ mount â†’ umount
Check phone â†’ Check folder â†’ Check RAM â†’ See drives â†’ Plug SD â†’ Unplug SD

df -h  â†’ Check total disk/phone storage
du -sh  â†’ Check size of a specific folder or app
free -m â†’ Check remaining RAM
lsblk  â†’ List all storage devices (internal + external)
mount  â†’ Attach / mount a storage device
umount  â†’ Safely detach / unmount a storage device

