DevOps / Interview Must-Know (Command Logic)
==================================

Pipe â†’ Output flow | > overwrite â†’ >> append | && success â†’ || fail


ps aux | grep nginx ------------List all processes â†’ only show nginx
echo "Hello" > file.txt----------Writes â€œHelloâ€ into file.txt, replacing old content       
echo "New line" >> file.txt----Adds â€œNew lineâ€ without removing old content
mkdir test && cd test---------Create directory â†’ go inside only if creation   succeeded
mkdir test || echo "Directory exists"--Try to create â†’ if fails, show message
